no one would dare dispute her word.

800
00:44:43,337 --> 00:44:45,362
Dispute her word.

801
00:44:45,539 --> 00:44:47,803
Excellency,
Her Highness would like to see you.

802
00:44:47,975 --> 00:44:49,408
