Isn't she?

803
00:44:49,577 --> 00:44:52,774
She can wait.
Not too long. She's packing up.

804
00:44:52,947 --> 00:44:55,939
Packing up?

805
00:44:57,218 --> 00:44:58,685
And where's Her Highness going?

806
00:44:58,853 --> 00:45:00,320
I don't know, and it doesn't matter.

807
00:45:00,487 --> 00:45:03,718
So, did you enjoy yourself today?
Yes. Until I became ashamed,

808
00:45:03,891 --> 00:45:06,052
Ashamed of allowing myself
to be put on display,

809
00:45:06,227 --> 00:45:08,422
Ashamed of conjuring up
tricks like a circus freak,

810
00:45:08,596 --> 00:45:11,190
Ashamed of asking people
to sign papers that I am real!

811
00:45:11,365 --> 00:45:12,525
I am real!

812
