819
00:45:26,881 --> 00:45:28,746
No one will ever be sure,
and you least of all.

820
00:45:28,916 --> 00:45:30,440
I know that today, too.
Wrong.

821
00:45:30,618 --> 00:45:32,210
Those people today
were not worth your efforts,

822
00:45:32,386 --> 00:45:33,444
But there is someone who is.

823
00:45:33,621 --> 00:45:35,816
One word from her,
and they will all grovel.

824
00:45:35,990 --> 00:45:37,958
The dowager empress, maria feodorovna.

825
00:45:38,125 --> 00:45:40,218
Grandmama.
Grandmama.

826
00:45:40,394 --> 00:45:43,192
Grandmama.

827
00:45:43,364 --> 00:45:44,956
She'll never see me.
She will.

828
00:45:45,132 --> 00:45:46,258
How do you know?
I know she will.

829
00:45:46,433 --> 00:45:47,229
Words.

830
00:45:47,401 --> 00:45:49,528
Call me Schemer, Plotter.
Call me what you will,

831
00:45:49,703 --> 00:45:51,295
But deep down, you know that if anyone

832
00:45:51,472 --> 00:45:53,565
Can get you to see that old woman,
it is I.

833
00:45:53,741 --> 00:45:55,971
I'll get you there for your sake.

834
00:45:56,143 --> 00:45:57,303
For my sake?

835
00:45:57,478 --> 00:46:00,845
You never did anything
for the sake of anybody but yourself.

836
00:46:01,015 --> 00:46:03,848
You enjoy playing with people,
making fools of them!

837
