That's why you're doing it... as a joke!

838
00:46:05,753 --> 00:46:07,277
To prove that you are great and alive

839
00:46:07,454 --> 00:46:09,684
And the others are small and dead!
Yes, and for money!

840
00:46:09,857 --> 00:46:14,851
Go ahead. It won't hurt.

841
00:46:15,963 --> 00:46:18,955
Sit down.

842
00:46:22,636 --> 00:46:27,335
If you want to leave after I am through,
I won't force you to stay.

843
00:46:27,508 --> 00:46:29,373
Let us say you are right.

844
00:46:29,543 --> 00:46:31,738
As a matter of fact, you are.

845
00:46:31,912 --> 00:46:33,675
But that's all the more reason
for you to go with me

846
00:46:33,847 --> 00:46:36,145
To the empress in Copenhagen.

847
00:46:36,317 --> 00:46:38,842
Never trust anyone who functions
from noble motives.

848
00:46:39,019 --> 00:46:40,247
The good are never sure,

849
00:46:40,421 --> 00:46:41,888
And in the end, they'll let you down.

850
00:46:42,056 --> 00:46:44,354
Our motives are different, agreed.

851
00:46:44,525 --> 00:46:50,828
But our goal is the same,
And that's the only thing that counts.

852
00:46:50,998 --> 00:46:56,994
Well, we'll go to Copenhagen?

853
00:46:58,072 --> 00:46:59,869
I had a dream the other night.

854
00:47:00,040 --> 00:47:03,771
Yes. About your father
being a ringmaster.

855
00:47:03,944 --> 00:47:07,004
No. This time he was a dollmaker.

856
