00:50:05,659 --> 00:50:06,387
Nothing special.

904
00:50:06,560 --> 00:50:08,755
We have it every day
the king is here in Copenhagen.

905
00:50:08,929 --> 00:50:11,659
Thank you.
The king?

906
00:50:11,832 --> 00:50:14,562
Uncle Chris, cousin to grandmama,
the Empress.

907
00:50:14,735 --> 00:50:18,728
Good. Very good.

908
00:50:33,253 --> 00:50:37,246
Excuse me, sir.

909
00:50:38,992 --> 00:50:40,721
Will you see Mrs. Anderson
to her rooms, please?

910
00:50:40,894 --> 00:50:43,158
Yes, sir.
Excuse me, please.

911
00:50:43,330 --> 00:50:48,290
Where is the bar?
That way, sir.

912
00:50:48,468 --> 00:50:50,265
Well?
Not good.

913
00:50:50,437 --> 00:50:51,233
Uh-uh.

