refuses to see you,

915
00:50:53,941 --> 00:50:56,535
Let alone her.
And him?

916
00:50:56,710 --> 00:50:58,109
No. Uh-uh.

917
00:50:58,278 --> 00:51:01,304
Our Prince Paul lives
on the old lady's allowance.

918
00:51:01,481 --> 00:51:03,039
He was always rather courageous.

919
00:51:03,217 --> 00:51:05,014
One possibility...

920
00:51:05,185 --> 00:51:07,210
Remember Baroness Von Lievenbaum,

921
00:51:07,387 --> 00:51:09,617
That crazy lady-in-waiting
to the empress?

