Just as the empress said you would.
Where is she?

946
00:52:50,490 --> 00:52:51,548
The empress?

947
00:52:51,725 --> 00:52:54,193
She's playing solitaire
with her memories.

948
00:52:54,361 --> 00:52:56,226
No, dear general, Anastasia...

949
00:52:56,396 --> 00:52:57,761
Or should I say Her Highness?

950
00:52:57,931 --> 00:52:59,899
Is it really she? I long to meet her!

951
00:53:00,067 --> 00:53:01,125
And so you shall,

952
00:53:01,301 --> 00:53:03,769
As soon as she is properly
introduced to Copenhagen.

953
00:53:03,937 --> 00:53:05,734
What a look you have.

954
00:53:05,906 --> 00:53:08,374
How inevitable that I'm useless to you.

955
00:53:08,542 --> 00:53:09,031
Why?

956
00:53:09,209 --> 00:53:11,268
The empress will never
receive you or that woman.

957
00:53:11,445 --> 00:53:13,538
You know her, an unmeltable icicle.

958
00:53:13,714 --> 00:53:15,443
Thank you.

959
00:53:15,615 --> 00:53:17,845
