00:53:27,627 --> 00:53:29,925
Surely you must have a pleasant life
with the empress

966
00:53:30,097 --> 00:53:32,827
With Her Majesty,
life is one eternal glass of milk.

967
00:53:32,999 --> 00:53:35,661
Oh, come. There must be some court life.
Not a crumb.

968
00:53:35,836 --> 00:53:37,030
She never entertains?

969
00:53:37,204 --> 00:53:40,139
Her phantoms,
the ghosts of her dead family.

970
00:53:40,307 --> 00:53:44,243
But she must go out for a drive
or shopping or a muse

971
00:53:44,411 --> 00:53:47,244
If you ever speak, whisper,
breathe one word...

