as possible tonight.

979
00:54:18,044 --> 00:54:18,976
Oh.

980
00:54:19,146 --> 00:54:21,512
He's quite a simple soul,
really... Prince Paul.

981
00:54:21,681 --> 00:54:23,512
His vocation and avocation
are one in the same...

982
00:54:23,683 --> 00:54:25,082
The pursuit of beautiful women.

983
00:54:25,252 --> 00:54:27,117
If you thought it necessary,
I suppose you would even

984
00:54:27,287 --> 00:54:31,280
To a plastic surgeon.

985
00:54:36,563 --> 00:54:37,825
Take your seat.

986
00:54:37,998 --> 00:54:40,091
Do you know how long it is
since I've been to a theat

987
00:54:40,267 --> 00:54:47,764
Don't display too much excitement.
Sit down.

988
00:54:49,042 --> 00:54:50,907
General, they just arrived.

989
00:54:51,077 --> 00:54:55,571
She, too?
Yes.

990
00:55:11,431 --> 00:55:15,925
Program.
Your Majesty.

991
00:55:19,406 --> 00:55:21,135
The box nearest the stage.

992
00:55:21,308 --> 00:55:22,832
The man you want me
to look beautiful for?

993
00:55:23,009 --> 00:55:24,567
