My fiance?

994
00:55:24,744 --> 00:55:26,803
The lady next to him
is Baroness Von Lievenbaum,

995
00:55:26,980 --> 00:55:29,380
Lady-in-waiting to the empress.

996
00:55:29,549 --> 00:55:30,811
And where's the empress?

997
00:55:30,984 --> 00:55:35,250
In the back of the box,
behind the curtain.

998
00:55:35,422 --> 00:55:41,190
So close after so many years.

999
00:55:41,361 --> 00:55:47,357
Oh, I am suddenly frightened.

